---
description: Use shared color tokens, avoid hardcoded colors
globs:
  - "compose/src/commonMain/kotlin/**/*.kt"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Do not hardcode colors in Compose feature components (avoid `Color(0x...)` in UI files).
- Use `ConektaColors` for semantic Compose colors.
- Use `CDNResources.Colors` + `colorFromHex(...)` for shared/CDN-defined tokens.
- When introducing a new semantic UI color, add it to `compose/theme/ConektaColors.kt`.
- When introducing a new cross-module token, add it to `shared/.../CDNResources.Colors`.
